      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRECIOUS COOKIE (7) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with three wins and a placing from five tries. Scored by one length last time (20.05) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. GOLDEN LABEL (1) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, one length from the winner PRECIOUS COOKIE (20.12) at this track. Can feature again. WHISKY ADDICTION (6) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 20.07 beating PASS THE PEPPA. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. CASH SIGN (2) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
